properties.areaDesc: East Bay Interior Valleys; East Bay Hills and the Diablo Range; North Bay Mountains
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 29 at 3:58AM PST until March 2 at 9:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 45 mph
expected.

* WHERE...North Bay Mountains, East Bay Interior Valleys and
East Bay Hills and the Diablo Range.

* WHEN...From 10 AM Sunday to 9 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS....Fuels are at record dry levels. Use
extreme caution with ignition sources and any outdoor burning.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM SUNDAY TO 9 AM PST MONDAY
